<li class="media">
  <div class="pull-left">
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-volume-down media-object"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="media-body">
    <div class="notification-body">
      {% set data = notification.content %}
      您上传到云存储的视频文件<strong>{{ data.filename }}</strong>已完成视频格式转换，快去<a href="{{ path('course_learn', {id:data.courseId}) }}#lesson/{{data.lessonId}}" target="_blank">看看</a>吧！
    </div>
    <div class="notification-footer">
      {{ notification.createdTime | date('Y-n-d H:i:s') }}
    </div>
  </div>
</li>